definitions.definition: ( usually uncountable ) A black, oily, sticky, viscous substance, consisting mainly of hydrocarbons derived from organic materials such as wood, peat , or coal.

subdefinitions.definition: ( uncountable ) A solid residual byproduct of tobacco smoke.

definitions.definition: ( slang , dated ) A sailor , because of the traditional tarpaulin clothes .
( uncountable ) Black tar , a form of heroin .
